dom]].\n\n==Results==\n\n===Placements===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n! Final results\n! Contestant\n|-\n| '''Miss International 1973'''\n|\n* '''{{flag|Finland}}''' - '''[[Anneli Bj\u00f6rkling]]'''\n|-\n| '''1st runner-up'''\n|\n* '''{{flag|United Kingdom}}''' - Zoe Spink\n|-\n| '''2nd runner-up'''\n|\n* '''{{flag|Iceland}}''' -  Helga Eldon Jonsd\u00f3ttir\n|-\n| '''3rd runner-up'''\n|\n* '''{{flag|Spain|1945}}''' - Maria Lorenzo\n|-\n| '''4th runner-up'''\n|\n* '''{{flag|Philippines}}''' - Maria Elena Suarez Ojeda\n|-\n| '''Semi-finalists'''\n|\n* '''{{flag|Argentina}}''' - M\u00f3nica Neu\n* '''{{flag|Australia}}''' - Paula Whitehead\n* '''{{flag|Colombia}}''' - Tulia G\u00f3mez Porras\n* '''{{flag|France}}''' - Christine Schmadth\n* '''{{flag|Germany}}''' - Ingeborg Braun\n* '''{{flag|Japan|1947}}''' - Miki Yaita\n* '''{{flag|New Zealand}}''' - Teresa Hodgson\n* '''{{flag|Switzerland}}''' - Dunya Claudia Wiederkehr\n* '''{{flag|Thailand}}''' - Jintana Te-chamaneewat\n* '''{{flag|Venezuela}}''' - [[Hilda Carrero|Hilda Carrero Garc\u00eda]]\n|}\n\n==Contestants==\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* '''{{flag|Argentina}}''' - M\u00f3nica Elena Neu\n* '''{{flag|Australia}}''' - Paula Lesley Whitehead\n* '''{{flag|Austria}}''' - Roswitha Kobald\n* '''{{flag|Belgium}}''' - Fiona Letta\n* '''{{flag|Bolivia}}''' - Rosa Maria Columba Gonz\u00e1lez\n* '''{{flag|Brazil}}''' - Denise Penteado Costa\n* '''{{flag|Canada}}''' - Nancy Henderson\n* '''{{flag|Chile}}''' - Ethel Klenner Rodr\u00edguez\n* '''{{flag|Colombia}}''' - Tulia In\u00e9s G\u00f3mez Porras\n* '''{{flag|Denmark}}''' - Anette Grankvist\n* '''{{flag|Ecuador}}''' - Pim Sanchez\n* '''{{flag|Finland}}''' - [[Anneli Bj\u00f6rkling]]\n* '''{{flag|France}}''' - Christine Schmadth\n* '''{{flag|Germany}}''' - Ingeborg Braun\n* '''{{flag|Greece|1970}}''' - Mariella Digiakomou\n* '''{{flag|Guam}}''' - Elaine Marques\n* '''{{flag|Hawaii}}''' - Marygold Toibinson\n* '''{{flag|Holland}}''' - 